data.description: Fabulous corner lot home in the highly sought after neighborhood of Heritage South one way in and one way out. Tree covered streets and well-manicured. This is a gem and won't last long! The home has an open floor plan for holiday get togethers as well as a bright Florida room that extends out to the covered back porch. The lg Master bedroom has wood floors and a very large walk-in shower. The secondary rooms are a good size and are connected by a Jack and Jill bathroom. The large laundry room has plenty of counter space for folding clothes. This homes solid brick exterior with beautiful landscaping and front porch is great for relaxing evenings. Let's not forget the entertainers dream backyard with in-ground POOL! Perfect for family and friends all year long! There also is a shed for all your gardening needs. Roof is 1 yr old and gutters in front have covers on them.  CALL FOR YOUR APPOINTMENT TODAY!
